{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "_comment": "gil-ads-audit-mcp v0.2.0 — Meta 광고 audit 전담 MCP 서버 manifest. REQ-AUDIT-MCP-004. 라운드 4 잔여 7 도구 구현 완료.",
  "_attribution": "Methodology adapted from agricidaniel/claude-ads v1.5.1 under MIT. See .claude/rules/moai/NOTICE.md §'agricidaniel/claude-ads (MIT)'.",
